Subsequently, both the labeled and pseudo labeled data are exploited to\npre-train a DNN, which is then fine-tuned based on the labeled channel records.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 08:05:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-26"}
