ave function overlap without changing the slope of\ntheir correlation. On the other hand, for a given nanoparticle overall\nthickness, dot/rod systems with a small CdSe core exhibit the strongest\ninfluenceability by surface charges.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Jul 2018 14:16:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Feb 2019 15:44:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-25"}
