-magnitude of stars\nprovide a valuable tool to measure the GC ages and offers a new venue to\ndetermine their absolute age to sub-Gyr accuracy with next generation IR\ntelescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 18:00:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
